messages.speaker: therapist
messages.text: Hi! I'm Anita Bhargava. Financial storytelling with cultural depth & modern vision. I'm here to help you understand your financial lifestyle and goals. To get started, could you please tell me your name?

messages.speaker: therapist
messages.text: Namaste Anika, beta! At 23, you're at such an auspicious time in your journey - where the colors of tradition can blend beautifully with your modern aspirations. Tell me your story - every financial journey has beautiful layers. Let's start with three key areas of your life: Where do you currently call home? How do you spend your precious free time? And what does a typical day look like for you? Understanding these threads will help us weave a tapestry of your ideal life.

notes.note: Client is Anika, 23 years old, beginning lifestyle assessment
